The paper discusses the use of stochastic neurons in deep learning models and proposes novel solutions for estimating or propagating gradients through them. This topic is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
